extends ../layouts/main

block title
    | Enroll 2FA

block header
    p
        a(href="/account/2fa") Back to 2FA settings
    h1 Passkey

block content
    p You're enrolling a&nbsp;
        strong security key
        | .

    p Would you like to set this up as a passkey?

    ul
        li
            a(href="/account/2fa/enroll?type=key&passkey=yes") Yes, allow signing in with just this security key
        li
            a(href="/account/2fa/enroll?type=key") No, just use my security key as a second factor
